fields.what_happened: In this stage of your life you accepted your first job. This is an important first step into your financial future. Usually, your first job is the first large source of stable income you have in your life. This money will allow you to find opportunities and start moving your life in the direction you want it to go. However, to fully take advantage of it, you will need to plan.
